      "payments": "Payments",
      "account": "Account",
      "consumer1Q": "How does Bellu work?",
      "consumer1A": "Bellu is a beauty and aesthetics marketplace. You search for professionals near you, view portfolios and real reviews, and book in just a few taps — no calls, no waiting.",
      "consumer2Q": "Do I need to pay to use it?",
      "consumer2A": "No! The app is 100% free for consumers. You only pay for the booked service, directly to the professional.",
      "consumer3Q": "Can I cancel a booking?",
      "consumer3A": "Yes. Each professional sets their cancellation policy. Usually you can cancel at no cost up to 24h before.",
      "consumer4Q": "How do I know if the professional is trustworthy?",
      "consumer4A": "Professionals go through document verification. Also, reviews are only from clients who were actually served.",
      "pro1Q": "How much does it cost to register?",
      "pro1A": "Registration is free. Bellu charges a small commission only on bookings made through the app.",
      "pro2Q": "Do I need a business license?",
      "pro2A": "No. We accept independent professionals. Salons and clinics can use their business ID.",
      "pro3Q": "How do I receive my payments?",
      "pro3A": "Payments are received directly by you. Bellu supports bank transfer, card and in-person payment.",
      "pro4Q": "Can I manage my team?",
      "pro4A": "Yes! In the Pro Dashboard you can register team members, set commissions and view individual schedules.",
      "pay1Q": "What payment methods are accepted?",
      "pay1A": "In Brazil: Pix, credit/debit card and boleto via Mercado Pago. In Spain: card and SEPA via Stripe.",
      "pay2Q": "Is it safe to pay through the app?",
      "pay2A": "Yes! We use certified payment gateways (Stripe and Mercado Pago) with end-to-end encryption.",
      "account1Q": "How do I create my account?",
      "account1A": "Download the app and create your account with Google, Apple or phone. In less than 1 minute you can start booking.",
      "account2Q": "Can I use Bellu in another country?",
      "account2A": "Yes! Bellu operates in Brazil and Spain. The app automatically detects your country and shows local professionals and currencies."
